{"tid":2119699,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鐵了心反中! 英國先禁華為 再鎖定抖音為「中國情報部門」","createTime":"2020-07-22T08:49:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T09:08:43.000Z","uid":227801,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"41d42998326c649e8f4bb8d411b8950e8153bc56","tid":2119699,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T08:49:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-07-22/439416\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2020-07-22%2F439416&d=ubUSuZPfwFYlyx9%2FldNtB%2F4XLRjZdTHGp6sdrEQ6olc%3D&h=29519c71\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-07-22/439416</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在美國鎖定對華為供應鏈祭出新制裁後，英國政府日前宣布，基於安全考量禁止華為參與英國5G網路建設，營運商需在2027年全部撤換已經安裝的華為設備。這項決定意味英國與這家中國電信巨擘長達20年的夥伴關係即將告終。此外，英國保守黨近日鎖定抖音(TIKTOK)，將抖音視為極大威脅且非常接近「中國的情報部門」。<br />\n英國首相強生（Boris Johnson）日前主持國家安全委員會（NSC）會議，討論在英國的未來發展等議題，數位、文化、媒體暨體育大臣陶敦（Oliver Dowden）在國會宣布，基於安全考量，自今年12月31日開始，禁止再向華為購買5G設備，營運商需在2027年全部撤換已經安裝的華為設備。<br />\n英國「排華」的這項重大決定，將贏得華府稱許，但勢必會激怒北京。中國駐英國大使昨天就提出警告，英國對華為的決策若出現「髮夾彎」，將有損英國名聲，而將中國視為敵國，就得面對中國制裁。"},{"pid":"7b439326ed0032f758f5656933ee9b6618082549","tid":2119699,"uid":346701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T08:55:50.000Z","msg":"日出了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e01bfdbfe82810fc8a451f7f2b45a58c07dcdab3","tid":2119699,"uid":35084,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T08:59:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BjQiKPp.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBjQiKPp.gif&h=9c0828db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"770e983fdc6f0c17205a23b69bac0b07a36f2bff","tid":2119699,"uid":308915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T09:08:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yP8PRxt.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyP8PRxt.gif&h=c5c47be8&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}